text: Barbara Wilk-Ślizowska (born 4 February 1935) is a Polish gymnast. She competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics and the 1956 Summer Olympics, winning a bronze medal at the latter. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:Living people Category:Polish female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Poland Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Kraków Category:Olympic medalists in gymnastics Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Poland Category:Medalists at the 1956 Summer Olympics
title: Barbara Wilk-Ślizowska
